Description: Here is a Very Rare and Collectable BC Rich Warlock Electric Guitar,from the "Body Art Collection". .. This is a Limited Edition with "Skulls" Graphics on the Front. Only 1000 of these were ever scheduled to be made and some were not shipped due to factory paint errors. This Guitar is in Excellent Condition and comes from my Personal Collection. Plays and Sounds Terrific ! Rare from 2004... Less than 1000 ever made. The Body Art Collection included a selection of extremely limited edition electric guitars made by the guitar manufacturer B.C. Rich. The series is based on the company's 'platinum series' and was made over two years from January 2003 until December 2004. The classic B.C. Rich shapes were given a new look with various images. Each guitar in the series carries a unique serial number and a 'limited edition' plaque on the reverse of the guitar, incorporated into the bolt-on neck. Rare Collectible Guitar for BC Rich Fans. New Strings, Tunes Perfectly, Great Classic Warlock 3+3 Widow Headstock, String Thru Design. Plays extremely well with a super fast neck. Stays in Tune great. Some bumps and light scratches on back and a smallchip on back of Warlock Headstock. overall good condition7/10. Oiled the neck, did intonation and setup. This Ax is ready to rock...
